{Main innovations continued in the mail. The introduction of the stamp in 1940
started payment in advance by the sender. Express post per horse-drawn mail
coach had achieved an average speed of 15 km per hour. Therefore,
international post in Middle Europe reached its destination in two days.  
 Pest and Paris played a match from 1842- 46. Pest(h) can be described as the
flat side of the future Budapest. Its team was headed by Szen and Loewenthal.
